long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension saves you valuable time when searching for your favorite in-depth reviewer on YouTube. With this extension you can automatically search for Saabkyle04's videos direct from your browser, no need to go to YouTube. It puts you in the driver's seat of video searches.

Changes:
1. A slight change in appearance.
2. The extension now has direct links to "Saabkyle04's" website and his Facebook page.
